et=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531920\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 05, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sdd1665702981543.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sdd1665702981543.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sdd1665702981543.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sdd1665702981543\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Storing Characters in the DBMS\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Characters in meta character set Font 0 are sent to the DBMS as one-byte seven-bit characters in the range 32 through 126. Characters in Font 1 are sent as one-byte eight-bit characters in the range 160 through 254.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__context_w2069ab1b5b1_w2070ab1b5_w2071ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__p_d63476e1_d63477e1_d63478e1\">Each character mapped to Fonts 2 through 7 is sent to the database as a three-byte unit.</p>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__li_d27653e1_d27654e1_d27655e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">The first byte is a nonprintable character (decimal value 25) which indicates ‘shift font’.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__li_d27656e1_d27657e1_d27658e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">The second byte is a decimal value in the range 32 through 94 indicating into which font and shape to switch.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__li_d27659e1_d27660e1_d27661e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">The last byte is the seven- or eight-bit character.\n </span>\n</li></ol></section>\n<section class=\"section result body required-cleanup-multiple-ol-elements-in-topic-body\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__result_w2072ab1b5b5_w2073ab1b5_w2074ab1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__fig_d63479e1_d63480e1_d63481e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Example of Font and Shape Information</figcaption>\n<p class=\"p\">Normal character in the ‘V’ position of Font 6, that is, ‘6.V’:</p>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__fig_w2075ab1b5b5b1b5b1_w2076ab1b5b5b1b5_w2077ab1b5b5b1_w2078ab1b5b5_w2079ab1b5_w2080ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/font_and_shape.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__p_d63482e1_d63483e1_d63484e1\">When stored in the DBMS, font number and shape\n            definitions are combined in a single number. This is shown in the table. For example,\n            the number for a bold character in Font 4 is 36.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"9\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Font and Shape Numbers</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__1\">Shape </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" colspan=\"8\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2\">Font </th>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__3\"></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__4\">0 </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__5\">1* </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__6\">2 </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__7\">3* </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__8\">4 </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__9\">5* </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__10\">6 </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__11\">7* </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__1 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__3\">Normal </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__4\">0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__5\">0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__6\">2 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__7\">2 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__8\">4 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__9\">4 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__10\">6 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__11\">6 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__1 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__3\">Underline </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__4\">8 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__5\">8 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__6\">10 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__7\">10 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__8\">12 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__9\">12 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__10\">14 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__11\">14 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__1 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__3\">Italics </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__4\">16 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__5\">16 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__6\">18 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__7\">18 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__8\">20 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__9\">20 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__10\">22 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__11\">22 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__1 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__3\">Italics and underline </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__4\">24 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__5\">24 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__6\">26 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__7\">26 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__8\">28 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__9\">28 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__10\">30 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__11\">30 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__1 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__3\">Bold </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__4\">32 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__5\">32 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__6\">34 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__7\">34 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__8\">36 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__9\">36 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__10\">38 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__11\">38 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__1 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__3\">Bold and underline </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__4\">40 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__5\">40 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__6\">42 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__7\">42 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__8\">44 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__9\">44 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__10\">46 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__11\">46 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__1 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__3\">Bold and italics </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__4\">48 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__5\">48 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__6\">50 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__7\">50 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__8\">52 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__9\">52 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__10\">54 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__11\">54 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__1 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__3\">Bold, italics, and underline </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__4\">56 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__5\">56 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__6\">58 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__7\">58 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__8\">60 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__9\">60 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__10\">62 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__2 sdd1665702981543__table_d5546e1_d5547e1_d5548e1__entry__11\">63 </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__p_d63485e1_d63486e1_d63487e1\">Characters in the fonts marked with an asterisk are\n            always stored as eight-bit characters, that is, in the decimal range 160 through 255. If\n            Uniface encounters an even number in the second byte, it checks to see whether the\n            character in the third byte is seven or eight bits to determine in which of the two\n            possible font and shape numbers the character belongs.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__p_d63488e1_d63489e1_d63490e1\">Characters below decimal value 32 are only available\n            in Font 0. However, ten of these are reserved by Uniface.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"sdd1665702981543__note_dcs_fdh_hcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The characters in the nonprinting ASCII range\n            (decimal 0 through 31) are interpreted by Uniface and are not available for use in user\n            data.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1665702670477.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Meta Character Sets</a><p>Meta character sets are used for translating installable character sets and defining translation tables. In earlier versions of Uniface, meta character sets were used as internal character sets instead of Unicode.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531920\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531920\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Storing Characters in the DBMS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 05, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Storing Characters in the DBMS Characters in meta character set Font 0 are sent to the DBMS as one-byte seven-bit characters in the range 32 through 126. Characters in Font 1 are sent as one-byte eight-bit characters in the range 160 through 254. Each character mapped to Fonts 2 through 7 is sent to the database as a three-byte unit. The first byte is a nonprintable character (decimal value 25) which indicates ‘shift font’. The second byte is a decimal value in the range 32 through 94 indicating into which font and shape to switch. The last byte is the seven- or eight-bit character. Figure 1. Example of Font and Shape Information Normal character in the ‘V’ position of Font 6, that is, ‘6.V’: When stored in the DBMS, font number and shape definitions are combined in a single number. This is shown in the table. For example, the number for a bold character in Font 4 is 36. Table 1. Font and Shape Numbers Shape Font 0 1* 2 3* 4 5* 6 7* Normal 0 0 2 2 4 4 6 6 Underline 8 8 10 10 12 12 14 14 Italics 16 16 18 18 20 20 22 22 Italics and underline 24 24 26 26 28 28 30 30 Bold 32 32 34 34 36 36 38 38 Bold and underline 40 40 42 42 44 44 46 46 Bold and italics 48 48 50 50 52 52 54 54 Bold, italics, and underline 56 56 58 58 60 60 62 63 Characters in the fonts marked with an asterisk are always stored as eight-bit characters, that is, in the decimal range 160 through 255. If Uniface encounters an even number in the second byte, it checks to see whether the character in the third byte is seven or eight bits to determine in which of the two possible font and shape numbers the character belongs. Characters below decimal value 32 are only available in Font 0. However, ten of these are reserved by Uniface. Note: The characters in the nonprinting ASCII range (decimal 0 through 31) are interpreted by Uniface and are not available for use in user data. Related Links Meta Character Sets Meta character sets are used for translating installable character sets and defining translation tables. In earlier versions of Uniface, meta character sets were used as internal character sets instead of Unicode. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}